<emphasis box="[637,752,1946,1972]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="300">plumosum</emphasis>
Wuillot
</taxonomicName>
(in Wuillot &amp; Gillies) 1993 [
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gillies" authorityYear="1990" box="[1184,1304,1946,1972]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="300" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1184,1304,1946,1972]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="300">Afroptilum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], 
<taxonomicName authority="McCafferty 2000" authorityName="McCafferty" authorityYear="2000" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Maliqua" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="300" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abdallahi">
<emphasis box="[1329,1436,1946,1972]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="300">abdallahi</emphasis>
McCafferty 2000
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lugo-Ortiz &amp; McCafferty" authorityYear="1997" box="[361,456,1982,2008]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Maliqua" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="300" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[361,456,1982,2008]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="300">Maliqua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] and the new species described in this paper.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3354879/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="301" startId="2.[151,264,1824,1849]" targetBox="[170,1417,179,1796]" targetPageId="2">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1824,1957]" pageId="2" pageNumber="301">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,328,1824,1849]" pageId="2" pageNumber="301">FIGURES 1–10.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kimmins" baseAuthorityYear="1956" box="[335,582,1824,1848]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="301" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dentatum">
<emphasis box="[335,582,1824,1848]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="301">Potamocloeon dentatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 1, head and thorax of male imago from Uganda; 2, its abdominal sterna and terga; 3, abdominal sterna and terga of male imago from Mali; 4, abdominal sterna and terga of male subimago from Uganda; 5, hind leg of male imago; 6, subimaginal mesonotum; 7–10, genitals: 7, holotype; 8–9, specimens from Mali; 10, specimen from Uganda.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,611]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
The species names 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kimmins" baseAuthorityYear="1956" box="[413,517,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dentatum">
<emphasis box="[413,517,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">dentatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1815" box="[533,614,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[533,614,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wuillot, in Wuillot &amp; Gillies" authorityYear="1993" box="[636,751,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumosum">
<emphasis box="[636,751,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">plumosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gillies" authorityYear="1990" box="[767,887,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[767,887,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Afroptilum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="McCafferty" authorityYear="2000" box="[949,1056,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Maliqua" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abdallahi">
<emphasis box="[949,1056,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">abdallahi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lugo-Ortiz &amp; McCafferty" authorityYear="1997" box="[1071,1166,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Maliqua" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1071,1166,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Maliqua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] are regarded as subjective synonyms (
<bibRefCitation author="Jacobus, L. M. &amp; McCafferty, W. P. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L." box="[331,556,189,216]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="129 - 140" refId="ref6563" refString="Jacobus, L. M. &amp; McCafferty, W. P. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L. (2006) Taxonomy of Afrotropical Securiops, new genus, and Cloeodes Traver (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae). African Entomology, 14 (1), 129 - 140." type="journal article" year="2006">
Jacobus 
<emphasis box="[430,480,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">et al</emphasis>
. 2006
</bibRefCitation>
). Wuillot and Gillies (1993) did not originally compare 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wuillot, in Wuillot &amp; Gillies" authorityYear="1993" box="[1193,1436,189,215]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumosum">
<emphasis box="[1193,1436,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Afroptilum plumosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kimmins" authorityYear="1956" box="[208,401,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dentatum">
<emphasis box="[208,401,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeon dentatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; male imagines of these forms have identical structure of genitals, that testifies that they really belong to one and the same species. 
<taxonomicName authority="McCafferty 2000" authorityName="McCafferty" authorityYear="2000" box="[601,1008,261,287]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Maliqua" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abdallahi">
<emphasis box="[601,809,261,287]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Maliqua abdallahi</emphasis>
McCafferty 2000
</taxonomicName>
was originally described as larvae and compared with the larval description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wuillot, in Wuillot &amp; Gillies" authorityYear="1993" box="[603,846,297,323]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumosum">
<emphasis box="[603,846,297,323]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Afroptilum plumosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; most of the reported differences between these two species are inconsistent. However, it is possible that 
<taxonomicName authority="(McCafferty 2000)" authorityName="McCafferty" authorityYear="2000" baseAuthorityName="McCafferty" baseAuthorityYear="2000" box="[743,1239,333,359]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abdallahi">
<emphasis box="[743,1019,333,359]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Potamocloeon abdallahi</emphasis>
(McCafferty 2000)
</taxonomicName>
is a valid species characterized by colorless tracheae of tergalii, while 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kimmins" baseAuthorityYear="1956" box="[756,1030,369,395]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dentatum">
<emphasis box="[756,1030,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Potamocloeon dentatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wuillot, in Wuillot &amp; Gillies" authorityYear="1993" box="[1074,1189,369,395]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Afroptilum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumosum">
<emphasis box="[1074,1189,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">plumosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and the new species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kluge" authorityYear="2019" box="[151,297,405,431]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="edentatum">
<emphasis box="[151,297,405,431]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">P. edentatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp n. have well pigmented tracheae. The validity of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="McCafferty" baseAuthorityYear="2000" box="[902,1039,405,431]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abdallahi">
<emphasis box="[902,1039,405,431]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">P. abdallahi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is questionable, while its imago is unknown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,152,611]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">
In addition to these continental African species, four species were described from 
<collectingCountry box="[1181,1316,477,503]" name="Madagascar" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and originally placed in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Traver" authorityYear="1938" box="[465,569,513,539]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[465,569,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: 
<emphasis box="[588,697,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">portabilis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Lugo-Ortiz, C. R. &amp; McCafferty, W. P. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L." box="[708,973,513,539]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="208 - 211" refId="ref7627" refString="Lugo-Ortiz, C. R., McCafferty, W. P. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L. (1999) The small minnow mayfly genus Cloeodes Traver (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae) in Madagascar. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington, 101 (1), 208 - 211." type="journal article" year="1999">
Lugo-Ortiz 
<emphasis box="[845,899,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">et al</emphasis>
. 1999
</bibRefCitation>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Traver" authorityYear="1938" box="[993,1097,513,539]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[993,1097,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], 
<emphasis box="[1125,1253,513,539]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">bicoloratus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gattolliat, J. - L." box="[1263,1436,513,539]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="387 - 402" refId="ref6236" refString="Gattolliat, J. - L. (2001) The genus Cloeodes (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae) in Madagascar. Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 108, 387 - 402. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79636" type="journal article" year="2001">Gattolliat 2001</bibRefCitation>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Traver" authorityYear="1938" box="[161,265,549,575]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[161,265,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], 
<emphasis box="[288,388,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">freitagae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gattolliat, J. - L." box="[398,570,549,575]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="387 - 402" refId="ref6236" refString="Gattolliat, J. - L. (2001) The genus Cloeodes (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae) in Madagascar. Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 108, 387 - 402. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79636" type="journal article" year="2001">Gattolliat 2001</bibRefCitation>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Traver" authorityYear="1938" box="[590,694,549,575]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[590,694,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
], 
<emphasis box="[721,883,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">pseudogladius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Gattolliat, J. - L." box="[893,1065,549,575]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="387 - 402" refId="ref6236" refString="Gattolliat, J. - L. (2001) The genus Cloeodes (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae) in Madagascar. Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 108, 387 - 402. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79636" type="journal article" year="2001">Gattolliat 2001</bibRefCitation>
[
<taxonomicName authorityName="Traver" authorityYear="1938" box="[1084,1188,549,575]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Cloeodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1084,1188,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Cloeodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
]. 
<bibRefCitation author="Salles, F. F. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L. &amp; Sartori, M." box="[1215,1436,549,576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="93 - 111" refId="ref7722" refString="Salles, F. F., Gattolliat, J. - L. &amp; Sartori, M. (2016) Phylogenetic analyses of Cloeodes Traver and related genera (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae). Systematic Entomology, 41 (1), 93 - 111. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / syen. 12144" type="journal article" year="2016">
Salles 
<emphasis box="[1292,1345,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">et al</emphasis>
. (2016)
</bibRefCitation>
placed them in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Salles &amp; Gattolliat &amp; Sartori" authorityYear="2016" box="[437,599,585,611]" class="Insecta" family="Baetidae" genus="Potamocloeon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[437,599,585,611]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Potamocloeon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a separate subgenus 
<emphasis box="[865,985,585,611]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="302">Aquaediva</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Salles, F. F. &amp; Gattolliat, J. - L. &amp; Sartori, M." box="[992,1357,585,611]" pageId="3" pageNumber="302" pagination="93 - 111" refId="ref7722" refString="Salles, F. F., Gattolliat, J. - L. &amp; Sartori, M. (2016) Phylogenetic analyses of Cloeodes Traver and related genera (Ephemeroptera: Baetidae). Systematic Entomology, 41 (1), 93 - 111. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / syen. 12144" type="journal article" year="2016">Salles, Gattolliat &amp; Sartori 2016</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
